cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with image interpretation and matching, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper proposes to use scene text for semantic interpretation of images, which involves natural language processing techniques. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with matching advertisement images against their human generated statements, which can be seen as an information retrieval task. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes to learn an embedding of the visual channel into a semantic embedding space, which involves machine learning techniques. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the interpretation of images, which is a multimedia task.
